The '''Emergency Military Powers Act''' was an act passed by the [[Imperial Senate/Legends|Imperial Senate]] in either [[19 BBY/Legends|19]] or [[18 BBY/Legends|18 BBY]]. It was presumably a part of the [[Imperial Charter/Legends|Imperial Charter]], and was referenced by [[Decree 77-92465-001]].

